00:54:51.940 --> 00:54:53.240
that you've spoken off square

00:54:53.240 --> 00:54:54.540
with Washington's ammunition
the steer clear

00:54:54.540 --> 00:54:55.840
of national attachments
on the [inaudible]?

00:54:55.840 --> 00:54:57.140
&gt;&gt; Theo Christov: Right.

00:54:57.140 --> 00:54:58.440
So I think what all of
these Washington, Franklin,

00:54:58.440 --> 00:54:59.740
Adams are doing is reading very
carefully Vattel as opposed

00:54:59.740 --> 00:55:01.040
to they are endorsing every
single aspect of his theory.

00:55:01.040 --> 00:55:02.340
But I think in doing so, Vattel
really serves as an authority.

00:55:02.340 --> 00:55:03.640
And I've had conversations with the
other colleague fellow Will Slauter

00:55:03.640 --> 00:55:04.940
on the question of how Vattel
is being used as an authority.

00:55:04.940 --> 00:55:06.240
And I can say a little
bit more about that

00:55:06.240 --> 00:55:07.540
in a more extended answer, but
let me just say briefly that,

00:55:07.540 --> 00:55:08.840
what is a question of
authority and how Vattel

00:55:08.840 --> 00:55:10.140
in late 18th century is being
used as a political authority?

00:55:10.140 --> 00:55:11.440
And the really thing he's
being used as a source

00:55:11.440 --> 00:55:12.740
for intellectual ammunition, there
is a bit of a cherry picking going

00:55:12.740 --> 00:55:14.040
on in the sense that whatever is
being convenient from his treaties

00:55:14.040 --> 00:55:15.340 position:56%
in his theory, he is being used by
many of the frames to make arguments

00:55:15.340 --> 00:55:16.640
that would be useful to their ends.

00:55:16.640 --> 00:55:17.940
But fundamentally I think he's
being used as an authority

00:55:17.940 --> 00:55:19.240
and he's eventually addressed
as he's just the authority.

00:55:19.240 --> 00:55:20.690
I mean, Locke is another one
and Montesquieu is another one,

00:55:20.690 --> 00:55:22.100
but Vattel is a true authority
in the Law of Nations.

00:55:22.100 --> 00:55:23.400
So I do think that Washington--

00:55:23.400 --> 00:55:24.700
there is a certain selectivity
in which he is being used.

00:55:24.700 --> 00:55:26.060
And by the way, there's a lot
more engagements of correspondents

00:55:26.060 --> 00:55:27.360
that I just couldn't
really gage into.

00:55:27.360 --> 00:55:28.660
But that sort of-- that
there is a selective process

00:55:28.660 --> 00:55:29.960
in which he's being used.

00:55:29.960 --> 00:55:31.760
[Inaudible].

00:55:31.760 --> 00:55:34.810
