struggle with questions

00:59:11.390 --> 00:59:14.010
of diplomatic practice,
relations with other states,

00:59:14.010 --> 00:59:15.890
Vattel provided that for them.

00:59:15.890 --> 00:59:19.640
And I think that kind of
practicality aspect unlike Grotius

00:59:19.640 --> 00:59:23.610
who was much more embedded
in his context of Portuguese

00:59:23.610 --> 00:59:28.230
versus Spanish imperial rivalry
was much more distance and kind

00:59:28.230 --> 00:59:33.200
of less practical than
someone like Vattel.

